function Test-PyroToolIntegration {
    <#
    .SYNOPSIS
        üî• Test PYRO tool integration
    .DESCRIPTION
        Runs basic tests on all installed PYRO tools to verify functionality
    .PARAMETER TestDataPath
        Path to test data directory
    #>
